I have a couple of questions! 1. Do I have a bit forehead and 2. Why do you follow me? Genuinely. If I don’t share my feelings anymore - I’m sure a lot of you followed me for my “openness and honesty” but if I’m more private now, does it make you sad? I think I sense that from some of you. I don’t know how to keep a healthy balance - I do a lot of typing and then just deleting bc the internet is not safe to put vulnerable life things. I’m sorry! Or are you just here for updates? For music? For my face or my clothes? Plz share!

But being here really stimulates that part of your brain again! 7 year old dodie is in me and I keep finding myself imagining I’m really on another planet - or walking through Toy Story Land like I have shrunk! Super cooool super coooool I love it and what’s cooler is seeing my friends light up and seeing that in them too!!
